      • setResolveExpressions

        public void setResolveExpressions​(boolean resolveExpressions)
        By default, the CLI doesn't resolve expressions located in scripts locally. In order to have the expressions resolved locally, set this value to true.
        Parameters:
        resolveExpressions - True to resolve locally, false to resolve at server execution time.
